Greetings <%= @member.first_name %>!

  <form id="member-form" action="/members/<%= @member.id %>" method="POST" name="member_form">
    <p>Are you going to participate?</p>

    <input type="checkbox" name="member[active]" value="true">Yes<br>
    <input type="checkbox" name="member[active]" value="false">No

    <div id="no-response">
      <p>Bummer, maybe next year!</p>
    </div>

    <div id="member-yes-response">
      <p>Sweet! Provide some of your recent interests here so the person who "draws" you has some ideas:</p>
      <textarea id="member-interests" name="member[interests]" rows="4" cols="50" placeholder="e.g. ironic tee-shirts, justin bieber, programming, etc (keep the $30 budget in mind)"></textarea>
    </div>

    <p>Is <%= Member.find_by_member_id(@member.id).first_name %> going to participate?</p>
    <input type="checkbox" name="member[dependent]" value="true">Yes<br>
    <input type="checkbox" name="member[dependent]" value="false">No

    <div id="dependent-no-response">
      <p>Bummer, maybe next year!</p>
    </div>

    <div id="dependent-yes-response">
      <p>Sweet! Provide some of their interests here:</p>
      <textarea id="dependent-interests" name="member[interests]" rows="4" cols="50" placeholder="e.g. handy many, bonzis, grand theft redemption.."></textarea>
    </div>

    <input type="submit" value="Submit">
  </form>